title: West Vent
text: West Vent is one of the three small <a href="shield%20volcano">shield volcano</a>es located in the <a href="Tuya%20Volcanic%20Field">Tuya Volcanic Field</a> of the <a href="Northern%20Cordilleran%20Volcanic%20Province">Northern Cordilleran Volcanic Province</a>, <a href="British%20Columbia">British Columbia</a>, <a href="Canada">Canada</a>. It is <a href="Holocene">Holocene</a> in age and stands in relief above the surrounding area north of the <a href="Nazcha%20Creek">Nazcha Creek</a> and comprise the <a href="West%20Tuya%20lava%20field">West Tuya lava field</a>.
